      <section eId="sec_750_U">
        <num>750-U</num>
        <heading>Veterinary and agricultural production exclusions</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_750_U__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>is owned by a licensed veterinarian; or\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_750_U__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>is located on land used in agricultural production;\n  2. does not allow individual burials;\n  3. does not allow individual grave markers;\n  4. does not charge a maintenance fee for the care of pet graves; and\n  5. does not make any representation that pet graves will be cared for\nor that the land is dedicated;\nshall be exempt from the trust fund provisions provided by section seven\nhundred fifty-r of this article, the dedication provisions provided by\nsection seven hundred fifty-n of this article and the area requirement\nprovided by section seven hundred fifty-p of this article.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
